1.	PURPOSE
________________________________________
This document defines the Disaster Recovery (DR) and Business Continuity Plan (BCP) strategy for Azure Service Bus resources supporting the TTO platform.
The objective is to ensure Service Bus messaging infrastructure can be recovered within acceptable recovery objectives during a regional outage while minimizing operational impact to dependent applications and business processes.
