________________________________________
1.	Azure Service Bus namespace deployed in DR region.
2.	Geo-DR pairing configured between primary and secondary namespaces.
3.	Queue definitions replicated.
4.	Topic definitions replicated.
5.	Subscription definitions replicated.
6.	Authorization rules replicated.
7.	Shared access policies validated.
8.	Private endpoints configured.
9.	Network access rules validated.
10.	Monitoring enabled in DR region.
11.	Capacity sizing equivalent to production namespace.
12.	Application teams configured to use Geo-DR alias endpoint.
13.	Key Vault integration available for connection management.
14.	Runbooks documented and tested.
